            <history-note id="DLM187836"><amended-provision>Section 12(4)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM328867">section 37(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Public
